Export Table Data

The content of a table can be easily exported to the clipboard and pasted into another application, such as MS ExcelTM, MS WordTM or Notepad.

In the GEO Home tab, select the table from the Select Definition box.

Click Export. This will export the content of the table to the clipboard.

Open another application, such as MS ExcelTM, MS WordTM or Notepad, and Paste from the clipboard. This will bring in the table values exported from the clipboard.
